@MezoNetwork is a Bitcoin-obsessed crew building a wild ecosystem where you can unlock liquidity with mUSD and vibe through market chaos, believing BTC is the ultimate asset to bank on yourself. Mezo is developing an economic layer for Bitcoin, aiming to extend BTC's utility beyond just a store of value. The Mezo Matsnet Testnet is their testing environment, allowing developers and users to experiment with the network's features before the mainnet launch. The testnet operates with Chain ID 31611 and uses BTC as its native currency.

MezoNetworkâ€™s hyping BitcoinFi, pushing MUSD as the ultimate Bitcoin-backed stablecoin, and teaming up with StorkOracle for speedy DeFi apps! In preparation for the testnet launch, Mezo has onboarded experienced validators to ensure network security and performance. Notable validators include Solv, Encode, Validation Cloud, Hex Trust, StakingCabin, Node.Monster, and Lavender.Five. For real-time statistics and to explore the Mezo testnet, you can visit their blockchain explorer. Additionally, Mezo has initiated campaigns to engage users and developers. For instance, they launched a joint campaign with Layer3 on April 2, 2025, where participants can complete tasks to earn mUSD rewards after the mainnet launch.
